---
title: Note
---

<div class="space-y-6 max-w-prose">
  <div class="space-y-2">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-sage-10">Default</p>
    <%= render Note.new do %>This is a note. Use it as a callout for asides and context within posts.<% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="space-y-2">
    <p class="font-mono text-xs text-sage-10">Accent</p>
    <%= render Note.new(scheme: :accent) do %>This is an **accent** note for things worth emphasizing.<% end %>
  </div>
</div>
